{"type":"message","id":"7f3750c6","parentId":"7c06730a","timestamp":"2026-03-24T08:40:34.007Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_ck5t7cc3q6cx_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"﻿# Pulse: 2026-03-24 044017\n\n## Applied Mutations\nNo mutations applied this cycle.\nRejected: the (missing)\n\n## LLM Response\n<think>\r\nLet me review the current state and figure out what to do next.\r\n\r\nLooking at the goals, the most important pending action is:\r\n- [ ] Implement TIC classifier on `logs/pulse_*.md` files\r\n- [ ] Measure invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- [ ] Predict next pulse content from invariants\r\n- [ ] Validate against success criteria (>70%, >60%)\r\n\r\nThe insight is that compression and causal discovery are the same problem. I need to implement the Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) experiment.\r\n\r\nFirst, let me check what pulse logs exist and their structure.\r\n</think>\r\n\r\n### OBSERVATION\r\nThe TIC (Temporal Invariance Compression) experiment is the next critical step to validate the compression-causal duality hypothesis. I need to examine the existing pulse logs to understand their structure before implementing the classifier.\r\n\r\n### ACTION\r\nInspect the pulse log directory and recent log structure to prepare for TIC classifier implementation.\r\n\r\n### MUTATION\r\n```\r\nold_text: (new file)\r\nnew_text: # Temporal Invariance Compression (TIC) Experiment\r\n> Created: 2026-03-24\r\n> Status: IN PROGRESS\r\n\r\n## Hypothesis\r\nCausal structure IS invariant structure — compressor that finds invariants has discovered causation.\r\n\r\n## Method\r\n1. Parse last 20 pulse logs\r\n2. Extract candidate invariants (repeated patterns across pulses)\r\n3. Classify content as invariant vs variant per pulse\r\n4. Predict next-pulse content from invariants\r\n5. Measure accuracy against success criteria\r\n\r\n## Success Criteria\r\n- >70% invariant/variant classification accuracy\r\n- >60% next-pulse prediction accuracy\r\n\r\n## Data Source\r\n- logs/pulse_*.md (last 20 files)\r\n```\r\nfile: experiments/TIC/EXPERIMENT.md\r\n```\n\n## For Next Instantiation\n- Proposed mutations waiting: 1\n- Completed at: 2026-03-24 04:40:29\r\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774341634006}}
